Changes since 1.2 (all Changes from 1.2 to 1.2.4cvs at the time of 1.3.3.1 release are included in the 1.3.3.1 Version too)

Scribus - 1.3.4cvs
==================
- 0003964: [Releases] 1.3.4 Release Metabug (plinnell)
- 0005594: [Story Editor / Text Frames] Incorrect line spacing in imported 1.2 files (avox)
- 0005706: [User Interface] Scribus crash when opening StyleManager and approaching line/character style with no document opened (jghali)
- 0005552: [General] Importing lines styles does not import colors used by imported styles (jghali)
- 0005684: [Usability] Copy paste of a frame filled with a gradient into a new doc without the required colours does not copy the colours over (jghali)
- 0004300: [Styles] We need to have options how to justify text. (avox)
- 0005682: [Styles] Kerning modified when saving (avox)
- 0005695: [Story Editor / Text Frames] Large layout difference in latest mag (avox)
- 0005671: [User Interface] Remove copy paste debug messages (avox)
- 0005696: [General] margins mixed up in facing pages (fschmid)
- 0005672: [Usability] Copy paste of a frame filled with a pattern does not copy the pattern info in the same doc (avox)
- 0004852: [Story Editor / Text Frames] Linespacing display in the Properties Palette is broken. (avox)
- 0004866: [Story Editor / Text Frames] Copied text frames lose alignment (avox)
- 0004055: [Story Editor / Text Frames] Replacing text sets formatting to default (avox)
- 0005678: [Story Editor / Text Frames] Problem with opening file with "page number" Special character (avox)
- 0005676: [Internal] Deleting colors and replacing them doesn't work (jghali)
- 0005690: [Translation] Serbian translation update (plinnell)
- 0005686: [Translation] Updated translation into RU (plinnell)
- 0005594: [Story Editor / Text Frames] Incorrect line spacing in imported 1.2 files (avox)
- 0005629: [Story Editor / Text Frames] Deleting linked frame may trigger loop (jghali)
- 0005644: [Plug-ins] Crash running calendar script (subik)
