Scribus - 1.3.2
===============
- 0002869: [Integration] Please put Scribus on Ubuntu/Gnome into Graphics menu (malex)
- 0003082: [Website] Add News item into sf.net (plinnell)
- 0002362: [PPCOSX] Scribus hangs or crashes while searching for fonts (avox)

